snippet.title: Photogeist Albums: Case 0 - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Tara has an important delivery to make to Yorin Farm's Way...until an intriguing mission pops up! Now, it's up to her to decide how she wants to come out of this spooky adventure: gentle and kind or ruthless and unrelenting? 

Banish or Appease strange creatures known as "Geists" and uncover the mystery of what happened to poor Mr. Yorin! 

Music in trailer by Any Austin

Links:
itch Page: https://photogeist-albums.itch.io/photogeist-case0

Twitter: https://twitter.com/photogeist_dev

Official Discord: https://discord.gg/NSZsG5J6rs
